*Čudovište* je spavalo u dubokoj pećini. (The monster was sleeping in a deep cave.)

Čovek je bio iznenađen kada je video *čudovište*. (The man was surprised when he saw the monster.)

Svi su bili uplašeni kad je *čudovište* izašlo iz šume. (Everyone was scared when the monster came out of the forest.)

Mnogo ljudi je izbeglo kad su čuli za *čudovište*. (Many people fled when they heard about the monster.)

Malo dete je bilo zapanjeno od *čudovišta*. (The little child was awestruck by the monster.)